{"tid":2278613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯一名現役士兵涉值班期間槍殺三名軍人被通緝","createTime":"2020-11-09T09:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T21:50:31.000Z","uid":310867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d27a15ef97f6ff592edd5f2cb9c1b7a10e434336","tid":2278613,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/wionews/status/1325723582756917249?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwionews%2Fstatus%2F1325723582756917249%3Fs%3D21&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e9d7d3e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwionews%2Fstatus%2F1325723582756917249%3Fs%3D21&h=aac28bbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/wionews/status/1325723582756917249?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nA Russian serviceman killed three colleagues in a shooting on a base near the southern city of Voronezh, news agencies reported citing the military."},{"pid":"385ceffef9ce2fb750e4d17c9a5bd49d75448d67","tid":2278613,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:23:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559096-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559096-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=78ace355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559096-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=55db9650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559096-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯西部軍區表示，事發南部沃羅涅日州附近的軍事基地，一支部隊的值班士兵襲擊到來檢查執勤情況的部隊管理人員，這名士兵搶走上級的槍支後逃走，有三名軍人受致命槍擊。<br />\n<br />\n西部軍區表示，部隊指揮部正聯同執法部門對這名士兵展開緝捕。"},{"pid":"7a472b384dd3068e0411f7cfb022ef04a8acb7c7","tid":2278613,"uid":310867,"like":